Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:27.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:42.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:55.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:09.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艷麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:17.08,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:27.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
